           <p>The iPad is one of the most popular gadgets around, but most people who own one <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/14-things-you-can-do-with-your-ipad-2013-8">don't know everything this device can do</a>. The video below gives you a few quick and easy tricks that will make your iPad experience more productive. <strong></strong></p> 
           <p><strong>Click for sound</strong>.</p> 
